::Fenox::

Fenox watches D walk over to her, knowing that he was very sad over 
the deaths of his friends. But there was nothing anyone could do 
about it. They were dead and would be dead, especially if they were 
humans like D had claimed. Humans were badly designed, and very 
fragile, especially for collisions.

She turns around, entering the Iron Fist and motioning D to follow. 
He was pretty wild, but Fenox hoped he wasn't claustraphobic.
